{"snp4.3:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.3 ","snp4.3:0.2":"Dutthatthakasutta ","snp4.3:1.1":"Vadanti ve dutthamanapi eke, ","snp4.3:1.2":"Athopi ve saccamana vadanti; ","snp4.3:1.3":"Vadanca jatam muni no upeti, ","snp4.3:1.4":"Tasma muni natthi khilo kuhinci. ","snp4.3:2.1":"Sakanhi ditthim kathamaccayeyya, ","snp4.3:2.2":"Chandanunito ruciya nivittho; ","snp4.3:2.3":"Sayam samattani pakubbamano, ","snp4.3:2.4":"Yatha hi janeyya tatha vadeyya. ","snp4.3:3.1":"Yo attano silavatani jantu, ","snp4.3:3.2":"Ananuputthova paresa pava; ","snp4.3:3.3":"Anariyadhammam kusala tamahu, ","snp4.3:3.4":"Yo atumanam sayameva pava. ","snp4.3:4.1":"Santo ca bhikkhu abhinibbutatto, ","snp4.3:4.2":"Itihanti silesu akatthamano; ","snp4.3:4.3":"Tamariyadhammam kusala vadanti, ","snp4.3:4.4":"Yassussada natthi kuhinci loke. ","snp4.3:5.1":"Pakappita sankhata yassa dhamma, ","snp4.3:5.2":"Purakkhata santi avivadata; ","snp4.3:5.3":"Yadattani passati anisamsam, ","snp4.3:5.4":"Tam nissito kuppapaticcasantim. ","snp4.3:6.1":"Ditthinivesa na hi svativatta, ","snp4.3:6.2":"Dhammesu niccheyya samuggahitam; ","snp4.3:6.3":"Tasma naro tesu nivesanesu, ","snp4.3:6.4":"Nirassati adiyati ca dhammam. ","snp4.3:7.1":"Dhonassa hi natthi kuhinci loke, ","snp4.3:7.2":"Pakappita ditthi bhavabhavesu; ","snp4.3:7.3":"Mayanca mananca pahaya dhono, ","snp4.3:7.4":"Sa kena gaccheyya anupayo so. ","snp4.3:8.1":"Upayo hi dhammesu upeti vadam, ","snp4.3:8.2":"Anupayam kena katham vadeyya; ","snp4.3:8.3":"Atta niratta na hi tassa atthi, ","snp4.3:8.4":"Adhosi so ditthimidheva sabbanti. ","snp4.3:8.5":"Dutthatthakasuttam tatiyam. "}